<title>ITALY: Italy cabinet approves decree law on employment.</title>
<headline>Italy cabinet approves decree law on employment.</headline>
<dateline>ROME 1997-03-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Italian cabinet on Friday approved a decree law aimed at speeding up investment to create new jobs, Italian agriculture minister Michele Pinto said at the end of the cabinet meeting.</p>
<p>The decree aims to simplify procedures to free up public expenditure on jobs.</p>
